Mach 8 Flow Over a 6° Half-Angle Cone
Objective

Validate hypersonic flow predictions around a sharp cone and compare CFD shock angles with theoretical conical-flow solutions.

Case Parameters
Parameter	Value
Mach Number	8
Cone Half-Angle	6°
Flow Type	Compressible
Geometry	Axisymmetric Cone
Solver	Density-Based
Turbulence Model	SST k-ω (if turbulent)
Expected Physics
Attached conical shock wave
Shock angle greater than cone angle
Compression through the shock
Surface pressure rise
Hypersonic conical flow field
